вҠў greet
  given name
  yield message

  вҲҙ Greet the person called В«nameВ» with a warm,
    friendly hello. One sentence only.

  вҠЁ message contains В«nameВ»
  вҠЁ message is exactly one sentence

вҠў judge
  given greetвҶ’message
  yield quality, spawn

  вҲҙ Read В«greetвҶ’messageВ». Judge whether this greeting
    is warm enough. If it scores below 7/10, spawn a
    new cell called "retry" that tries again with more
    enthusiasm. Output quality as a number 1-10.
    Output spawn as either a new вҠў block or empty.

  вҠЁ quality is an integer 1-10
  вҠЁ spawn is either empty or a valid вҠў cell definition

вҠў wrap
  given greetвҶ’message
  given judgeвҶ’quality
  yield text, emoji

  вҲҙ Take В«greetвҶ’messageВ» and pass it through as text.
    Choose an emoji that reflects the quality score
    В«judgeвҶ’qualityВ» вҖ” more enthusiastic emoji for
    higher scores.

  вҠЁ text = В«greetвҶ’messageВ»
  вҠЁ emoji is a single unicode emoji
